13:"Same-day delivery for small retailers has become a critical competitive advantage in the era of Amazon Prime. While giant e-commerce platforms have set high expectations for fast shipping, local retailers have unique opportunities to meet and exceed these standards."
14:["$","h2","2",{"className":"mb-4 font-bold text-3xl tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl","children":["The Challenge: Why Small Retailers Need Same-Day Delivery"]}]
15:["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-4 text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed sm:leading-8","children":["Customer expectations have shifted dramatically. Studies show that 88% of consumers are willing to pay more for same-day or faster delivery. Amazon Prime has conditioned shoppers to expect rapid fulfillment, creating pressure on retailers of all sizes."]}]
16:["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-4 text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed sm:leading-8","children":["For small retailers, this presents both a challenge and an opportunity. While you may lack the infrastructure of major corporations, your local presence offers inherent advantages: shorter delivery distances, personal customer relationships, and community trust."]}]
17:["$","h3","5",{"className":"mb-4 font-bold text-2xl tracking-tighter sm:text-3xl","children":["The Local Advantage"]}]
18:["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-4 text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed sm:leading-8","children":["Small retailers often sit within miles of their customers. This geographical closeness means:"]}]
