25:["$","p","19",{"className":"mb-4 text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed sm:leading-8","children":["Start with a manageable delivery radius of 5-15 miles from your store. Consider traffic patterns, geographic barriers, customer density, and practical delivery time windows."]}]
