2e:["$","p","28",{"className":"mb-4 text-base text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed sm:leading-8","children":["Same-day delivery requires accurate, real-time inventory. Implement point-of-sale systems that update stock instantly, maintain safety stock levels, and integrate online and physical inventory."]}]
